<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">尾数逢9法，是指被乘数或乘数的尾数是9，或被乘数、乘数的尾数均为9。乘数尾数是9时，先取其超数与被乘数相乘，然后再减一个被乘数，即得其积，即为所求的积，可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">10am-m</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中被乘数为m，乘数超数的首位数字为a（乘数首位数字实际是a-1）。</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">78×69=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 78×69</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=10×7×78-78</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=10×546-78</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=5460-78</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=5382</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>